<沿革內容><![CDATA[1.On Sep.29,2022,Penghu National Scenic Area Management Office, Tourism Bureau, Ministry of Communications Guanpeng Beizi Order No. 11108004021 stipulates to publish 5 articles in full text; and since the Jan.1,2023 carry out.]]></沿革內容>
<前言><![CDATA[]]></前言>
<法規內容>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 1</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[These standards are formulated in accordance with Paragraph 1 of Article 10 of the Charges And Fees Act.]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 2</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The standards for Xiao Men Geological Discovery Hall are as follows:
1.General Admission: NT$30.
2.Discount Admission: NT$15.]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 3</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The following valid identifications as must be shown for Discount Admission:
1.Seniors over 65 years old (Holidays).
2.Students.
3.Voluntary police officers and voluntary firefighters with “Voluntary Service Honor Card”.
4.Groups with more than 10 people.]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 4</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The following valid identifications must be shown for Free Admission:
1.Children under 6 years old.
2.Seniors over 65 years old (Weekdays).
3.Off-campus education or academic promotion must apply and be approved by official documents in advance.
4.Government departments shall apply and be approved by official documents in advance to accommodate international guests.
5.Voluntary workers with ‘Voluntary Service Honor Card”.
6.Persons with disabilities and one essential companion.]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 5</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[This standard is effective from January 1, 2023.]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
</法規內容>
</法規>
